ues should be provided to the patient in writing after the patient\u2019s first attempt to answer. \n\nWritten category cues should state: \u201csock, something to wear; blue, a color; bed, a piece of furniture.\u201d \n\no  For C0300 items, instructions should be written as:", "type": "Document"}}